item.content:encoded:
Discover:

Pokemon xetrix

Some of the maps that i created:

Route 1 X

First route that the player will face, where he will also fight his rival Blue!

Valerion city

The player will have to use surf for the first time. Oh and there is also a casino available!

Volcano city

I hope you can sustain some heat because, well you are in an active volcano ...

Ice cave

After that volcano why not chill in this ice cave?

Route 7 X

Here the player will have to fight strong trainers and cross a waterfall.

Magenta plateau

Ah!Finally! You made it to the pokemon league!

Explore The World

You can explore the whole world, even the seas with the surf abilities. Oh and also you can fly anywhere you already visited!

Arenas in pokemon Xetrix

There are 4 different arena in Pokemon Xetrix (Aside from the pokemon league). Here is how they look like:

item.title: About
item.dc:creator: xetrix
item.content:encoded:
Who is the creator?

My mission:

I started playing pokemon since I was 5 years old and I always told myself that one day I will create my own pokemon game. So I experimented on Pokemon Xetrix and build my vision of an ideal pokemon game.

Since I initially created Pokemon Xetrix for me and my friends, there is alot of inside jokes in it, aside from my own jokes and sense of humor. Basically I made a Pokemon game to chill and have fun. I hope you enjoy it!

some additional contents

It's Time to Start Your Adventures!

Well, even gym leaders can be weird sometimes!

Guess you will have to do what the gym leader wants if you want to defeat him :/

https://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pokemon-step-on-plants_Trim.mp4
Random events

Random events can be found everywhere, you never know what can happen...

Pokemon battle

This is how a pokemon battle look. And remember, only cowards run away from a battle!

I made sure that my Pokemon game have a lot of similarity from real life.

So here you have a nice talk with a girl, everything is going well.

You decide to talk to her again aaaaand now she hates you...
